title: Circa Las Vegas
author: BundtCake_
pages:
The Circa Las Vegas
is the newest Hotel
and Casino opened up
in Downtown Las
Vegas, having had its
grand opening
ceremony on October
27th, 2020. As the
first ground up
casino to be built
downtown in over 40
years, it is a major
milestone in the
evolution of the City

of Las Vegas. It is
notable as being one
of the first hotels in
Las Vegas to be fully
only for people 21
and over.
